Utilites for samtools. 

Author:
	Pierre Lindenbaum PhD

WWW:
	http://plindenbaum.blogspot.com

Mail:
	plindenbaum@yahoo.fr




A set of tools using the samtools API:

- bamsorted: tests if a bam file is sorted. See http://plindenbaum.blogspot.com/2011/02/testing-if-bam-file-is-sorted-using.html
 
- selectflag: interactive dialog returning a SAM flag. See http://plindenbaum.blogspot.com/2011/07/interactive-dialog-generating-sam-flag.html

- ttview a text-based short reads alignment viewer writing to stdout. See http://plindenbaum.blogspot.com/2011/07/text-alignment-viewer-using-samtools.html

 - bam2wig: transforms a bam file to the UCSC wig format.
